  "signal_description": "The query retrieves data from the table 'defaultview-225'. It calculates the total amount of invoices in USD and the average cycle time for each month. The 'Month' column represents the month of the data. The 'Total Amount (USD) of Invoices' column shows the sum of the 'Inv. Converted USD Amount' column. The 'Avg. Cycle time' column calculates the average time between the 'end_time' of the 'Clear Invoice' event and the 'end_time' of the 'Post Invoice' event. The results are ordered in ascending order by the 'Month' column and filled with missing months using the 'timeseries' function."
